\begin_layout Standard
\noindent
It describes the plot of the 1981 film by the same name.
 Indiana Jones is the only one who knows where to find the Ark of the Covenant.
 He travels to Tanis to excavate it, but before he can return home he is
 intercepted by the Nazis.
 They believe the Ark will grant them power and open it, but instead its
 angelic guardians kill the Nazis, leaving Jones free to retake it and return
 home.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
