 We have replaced that with Sabre's model of belief.
 Because the Nazis could not have wrong beliefs about the outcome of opening
 the Ark, their goal in the original problem is that the Ark be open.
 In our version, their goal is to be immortal, and they have a wrong belief
 about the danger of opening the Ark, which is more in line with the film
 the problem is based on.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
